topic: Movie Workflow Series ("Tv series explorative search")

goals.1: Return the number of seasons and episodes per season of the tv series
goals.2: Get the number of episodes in which the cast members played a role. Who are the most present actors?
goals.3: Check who is the actor who acted in more films while working on "How I met your mother" and who is the actor who participated in more films after the end of the tv series.
goals.4: Compare HIMYM with the tv series "The Office (US)" in terms of number of seasons, episods and cast members.
goals.5: Return how many of the actors who are members of the cast of the tv series have [Kavin Bacon number](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Six_Degrees_of_Kevin_Bacon#:~:text=Kevin%20Bacon%20himself%20has%20a,Bacon%20number%20is%20N%2B1.) equal to 2

name: 86c32028f0

search_workflow.narrative:
start your workflow here
find predicate of the cast member ->P161
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { wd:Q23831 ?p ?o . FILTER(!isLiteral(?o)) ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . } LIMIT 5
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { wd:Q23831 wdt:P31 ?p . FILTER(!isLiteral(?o)) ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . } LIMIT 5
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426. ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . } LIMIT 5

search_workflow.narrative:
find properties of tv series   (number of episodes->P1113 , number of seasons->P2437)
(start time -> P580 , end time -> P582)
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; ?p ?o. ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . filter regex(?pName,"start|end",'i') } Order by ?p LIMIT 10

search_workflow.narrative: get number of seasons and episodes per season
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?tvseriesName ?episodes ?season WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P1113 ?episodes; wdt:P2437 ?season. ?tvseries <http://schema.org/name> ?tvseriesName . } LIMIT 5
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { wd:Q147235 ?p ?o . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . filter regex(?pName,"character",'i') } order by ?pName LIMIT 5
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { wd:Q147235 wdt:P674 ?role . ?role ?p ?o. ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . } order by ?pName LIMIT 5

search_workflow.narrative: get the number of episodes which the cast members played a role
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?castmemberName (sum(?episodes) as ?numberoffilms) WHERE { { SELECT DISTINCT ?castmemberName ?tvseries ?episodes WHERE { ?role wdt:P175 ?castmember. ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember; wdt:P1113 ?episodes.FILTER(isNumeric(?episodes)) ?castmember <http://schema.org/name> ?castmemberName . } } } order by desc (?castmemberName) LIMIT 5

search_workflow.narrative: the most present actors in films
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?castmemberName (count(?castmemberName) as ?numberoffilms) WHERE { { SELECT DISTINCT ?castmemberName ?tvseries WHERE { ?role wdt:P175 ?castmember. ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember; wdt:P1113 ?episodes. ?castmember <http://schema.org/name> ?castmemberName . } } } order by desc (?numberoffilms) LIMIT 5

search_workflow.narrative: find start an end of "How I met your mother" (start:2005 , end: 2014)
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?start ?end WHERE { wd:Q147235 wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 ?castmember; wdt:P580 ?start ; wdt:P582 ?end . } LIMIT 50

search_workflow.narrative: actor who acted in more films while working on "How I met your mother"
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?castmember ?castmemberName ?start ?end WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 ?castmember; wdt:P580 ?start ; wdt:P582 ?end . { SELECT DISTINCT ?castmember WHERE { wd:Q147235 wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 ?castmember. } group by ?castmember } FILTER(?start > "2005-09-19"^^xsd:dateTime && ?end < "2014-03-31"^^xsd:dateTime). ?castmember <http://schema.org/name> ?castmemberName . } group by ?castmemberName LIMIT 5

search_workflow.narrative: get the number of actor who acted in more films while working on "How I met your mother"
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?castmemberName (Count(?castmember ) AS ?numberoffilm) WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 ?castmember; wdt:P580 ?start ; wdt:P582 ?end . { SELECT DISTINCT ?castmember WHERE { wd:Q147235 wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 ?castmember. } group by ?castmember } FILTER(?start > "2005-09-19"^^xsd:dateTime && ?end < "2014-03-31"^^xsd:dateTime). ?castmember <http://schema.org/name> ?castmemberName . } order by desc (?numberoffilm) LIMIT 5

search_workflow.narrative: get the number of actor who acted in more films after "How I met your mother"
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?castmemberName (Count(?castmember ) AS ?numberoffilm) WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 ?castmember; wdt:P580 ?start ; wdt:P582 ?end . { SELECT DISTINCT ?castmember WHERE { wd:Q147235 wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 ?castmember. } group by ?castmember } FILTER(?start > "2014-03-31"^^xsd:dateTime). ?castmember <http://schema.org/name> ?castmemberName . } order by desc (?numberoffilm) LIMIT 5

SELECT DISTINCT ?tvseriesName ?episodes ?season (Count(?castmember ) AS ?numberofcastmember) WHERE { Values ?tvseries{ wd:Q147235 wd:Q23831 } ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 ?castmember; wdt:P1113 ?episodes; wdt:P2437 ?season. ?tvseries <http://schema.org/name> ?tvseriesName . } order by desc (?numberofcastmember)

SELECT DISTINCT ?castmember ?castmemberName WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 ?castmember. ?castmember <http://schema.org/name> ?castmemberName . filter regex(?castmemberName,"Kevin Bacon",'i') }

search_workflow.narrative: find all  members of the cast of the tv series have Kavin Bacon number equal to 1
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?tvseriesName ?castmemberName WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 wd:Q3454165. ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember. ?tvseries <http://schema.org/name> ?tvseriesName . ?castmember <http://schema.org/name> ?castmemberName . } order by ?castmemberName limit 50

search_workflow.narrative: find all tv series played by cast memebrs which have Kavin Bacon number equal to 1
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?tvseries ?tvseriesName WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember. { SELECT DISTINCT ?castmember WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 wd:Q3454165. ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember. } } ?tvseries <http://schema.org/name> ?tvseriesName . ?castmember <http://schema.org/name> ?castmemberName . } order by ?tvseriesName limit 50
output: A Good Day to Die Hard

search_workflow.narrative: find all  members of the cast of the tv series have Kavin Bacon number equal to 2
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?castmemberName ?tvseriesName WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember. { SELECT DISTINCT ?tvseries WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember. { SELECT DISTINCT ?castmember WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 wd:Q3454165. ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember. } } } } MINUS{ SELECT DISTINCT ?castmember WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember. { SELECT DISTINCT ?castmember WHERE { ?tvseries wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426; wdt:P161 wd:Q3454165. ?tvseries wdt:P161 ?castmember. } } } } ?tvseries <http://schema.org/name> ?tvseriesName . ?castmember <http://schema.org/name> ?castmemberName . } order by ?tvseriesName limit 500
